===Noun===
'''Noob''','''noob''','''n00b'''

# A noob is someone who has an apparent lack of ability in a certain field. Especially in online gaming, where a noob is a person who has been playing for a long time but still only possesses similar skills to a newbie.
#:Example: ''You are a major noob.''


